name: HUGE DMND WAVE
description: I saw my friend just bought an Ipad Air 2020, I really wanted it for so long, so i asked her to lend me her Ipad then I try to draw some lines on procreate, and I felt " oh damn this is super cool " been dreaming of having this device so damn much, she said she will sell her Ipad because she was just bored with it, and I wish I could pay this device so I can make more more cool artwork. Hic Et Nunc Please do your Magic!.
